{"tid":1911554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（YouTube戰線）手足無懼CCTVB追擊 另開新頻道串鳩CCTVB","createTime":"2020-03-05T11:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T21:03:03.000Z","uid":291448,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee27b201116ea02b6f15d5a75a0ffbdfd0960c3","tid":1911554,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"呢位手足個頻道名叫高手紹2.0:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjIlBU5MMD5Qw6e63EedvBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCjIlBU5MMD5Qw6e63EedvBg&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c927a994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjIlBU5MMD5Qw6e63EedvBg</a><br />\n之前佢嘅主頻道因為拍左條串柒CCTVB嘅片而比CCTVB<br />\n以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">版權理由剷咗佢條片 兼且收埋版權警告<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mq3sDdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMq3sDdo.png&h=22608b0e&s={SIZE}\" /></span></strong><br />\n所以佢另開一個頻道專門拍D串柒CCTVB嘅片<br />\n就係叫高手紹2.0啦 以下係佢嘅作品<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ecnAXRJVF1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FecnAXRJVF1g&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=a0110cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ecnAXRJVF1g</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D4yxECT5E6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD4yxECT5E6U&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=4bba56c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D4yxECT5E6U</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nKhuwmUFC7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnKhuwmUFC7k&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ca18c406\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nKhuwmUFC7k</a><br />\n大家大大力咁懲罰佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf227ecba86a6bb67777e52dcf6e329d12e90fc","tid":1911554,